article.headline: Winthrop 52, Austin Peay 36
article.story: CHARLOTTE AMALIE, U.S. Virgin Islands (AP) -- James Shuler scored 13 points and Winthrop took third place in the Paradise Jam tournament with a 52-36 victory over Austin Peay on Monday night. Winthrop forced 22 turnovers and opened the second half with a 15-4 to take control. Maurice Hampton had 13 points for Austin Peay.
